- Any constants from math or numpy modules.

### How to Ensure Uniqueness:

Each of your 10 functions must use a unique combination of operations. For example, one function could use the exponential of the remaining space, another could use the logarithm of the remaining space, another could use the ratio of the item to the remaining space, and so on.

### How to Test Your Functions:

Once you've written your functions, you can test them with sample bins and items to see how they behave. For example:

